<paragraph id="91AF56A698345AF0F5EA171208735E4E" pageId="52" pageNumber="77">Thailand: Lampang, Phetchabun, Kanchanaburi, Prachuap Khiri Khan, Saraburi, Phatthalung, Trang, Satun, Songkla. India, Laos, Myanmar, Vietnam, Malay Peninsula, Malay islands.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
